title: 239: Who is the most dangerous playoff bubble team?
itunes:title: 239: Who is the most dangerous playoff bubble team?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks give you the players to watch for the biggest matchups this weekend. The guys also explain how Adam Thielen has found so much success this season. DJ and Bucky then pick the franchises in the hunt that your team doesn't want to see come playoff time.
